{"tid":1683072,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple AirPods Pro 耳機已被破解，同零件華強北僅賣 300 元！","createTime":"2019-10-30T12:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T23:37:14.000Z","uid":58335,"like":11,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"77eaccf7e212a4174e28443392569b0738ce85f1","tid":1683072,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"Apple 前晚在沒有先兆之下，突然在官網上架了最新的 AirPods Pro 無線耳機。對於該耳機，售價比第二代 AirPods 貴了 700 多元，售價 1,999 元。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/airpods-pro-hands-fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2Fairpods-pro-hands-fb.jpg&h=dcce5cc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接近 2 千元的價格對不少人來說還是難以接受的，所以靠破解仿製為生的中國大陸電子廠又開始發力了。有消息稱目前華強北已經做出了與 AirPods Pro 同款模具的样機，售價可能不到 300 元人民幣就可以拿到，現時國內廠商 TWS 就是其中的代表。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/3378f6c60ed0e6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F3378f6c60ed0e6f.jpg&h=3ba404aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國產的無線耳機仿製品價格低，質量也肯定沒有正品那麼好，但就恰恰符合大部分人不捨得花錢但又貪慕品牌效應的用家，所以就造就了大量的市場。不想用原價買正貨，但又想體驗 Apple 的產品，這就是高仿 AirPods 存在的原因了。<br />\n<br />\n從目前的消息來看，華強北已經製作出 AirPods Pro 的高仿版，有著相同的模具和样機，就等著後續的測試上市了，預計在 300 元左右，往後相會有更多仿製品推出，售價將會壓至更加低，幾十元就有。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/10/30/china-airpods-pro-clone-300-dollars-only/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F10%2F30%2Fchina-airpods-pro-clone-300-dollars-only%2F&d=VY3E9QkOBFFWjsPhNJvPHsF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=ff5ffda2\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/10/30/china-airpods-pro-clone-300-dollars-only/</a>"},{"pid":"0c7a1078e2645f7d30f3372e2f252f8892c4361d","tid":1683072,"uid":323913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T12:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57290a9086a1cd1f3